_sText:
This is pack of pillars which can be used to hold up a walkway or other such things

One pillar contains a light which glows through parts of it, another one is multiple cylinders stacked on top of each other, There is one which is multiple squares which are stacked on top of each other in a spiral and the final one is spikes which converge on each other these would be good in a ice cave or something made of glass.

All feedback is appreciated.   

!!Please Vote!!
